f END in 12 minutes making it almost 20DPS difference when those 12 minutes are up. This is of course in addition to taps, heals, snares, etc.  This is just ANOTHER case where the expansion has further enhanced knight tanking in single group settings more than warriors and its gone to the point where knights are BETTER in group settings than warriors.  You spend 10 mana per tick to cast Decrepit Skin, and given an average group probably regen somewhere around 30 per tick for a net GAIN of 20ish mana per tick.  Warriors spend about 59 Endurance per tick for Mock.  And gain back about 20 per tick while fighting.  For a net LOSS of almost 40 endurance per tick.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Edit:  But I'm with you on not making Aura of Runes the fix.  Aura of Runes does nothing level 65 or lower.  I shouldn't have to give up the ability to quickly tap Furious if my healer lags on a heal- instead having to click off Runes, then hit Furious.  I don't want to be a one trick pony only balanced against knights while my one trick is up, AND giving up Healing Will and Spirit of Rage (not that either are all that and a bag of chips, but why should I have to give them up just to be balanced?)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Heimdall-RN on &lt;span class="date_text"&gt;03-19-2006&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="time_text"&gt;01:56 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
